## Parking Sensor

The device detects stationed vehicles over the parking lot where it is installed to get real-time information about the parking spots' availability and usage thanks to magnetic detection technology. The device is installed directly on the ground so the vehicles can pass over it.

<img src={useBaseUrl('img/network-iot/devices/ready-to-use/iotsens/parking-sensor.jpg')} />

